      • compare

        public int compare(HwlocBitmap bitmap)
        Compare this bitmap object and bitmap using their highest index.

        Higher most significant bit is higher. The empty bitmap is considered lower than anything.

        Java binding of the hwloc operation hwloc_bitmap_compare().

      • compareFirst

        public int compareFirst(HwlocBitmap bitmap)
        Compare this bitmap object and bitmap using their lowest index.

        Smaller least significant bit is smaller. The empty bitmap is considered higher than anything.

        Java binding of the hwloc operation hwloc_bitmap_compare_first().
